OL,3,CHearts and Celtic fans get ready for
OL,4,Cpivotal league title clash
OL,6,FHearts and Celtic fans are eagerly
OL,7,Fawaiting the league title clash later
OL,8,Fon Saturday.
OL,10,FThe Scottish Premiership decider,
OL,11,Ftaking place at Celtic Park in
OL,12,FGlasgow, kicks off at 12.30 and if
OL,13,FHearts win it would mark the first
OL,14,Ftime for 66 years that they have taken
OL,15,Fthe trophy.
OL,17,FShould they win, Hearts are expected
OL,18,Fto celebrate on the streets of
OL,19,FEdinburgh on Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/2
