OL,3,CHearts and Celtic fans get ready for
OL,4,Cpivotal league title clash
OL,6,FCeltic have no official event if they
OL,7,Fwin, with Police Scotland stating on
OL,8,FFriday the team had not put any plans
OL,9,Fin place for official celebrations.
OL,11,FAn earlier match between Celtic and
OL,12,FMotherwell stirred some controversy
OL,13,Fover a penalty disputed by fans.
OL,15,FA 19-year-old man has been arrested
OL,16,Fand charged after referee John Beaton
OL,17,Fhad his personal details leaked in the
OL,18,Fwake of the penalty, Police Scotland
OL,19,Fsaid.
